@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gcosav(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp((v2 + 0.06 / v1 + 0.17)))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.exp((v2 + 0.63 * tmp + 0.06)))
    v0 = (0.78 * 0.50)
    v2 = ((0.02 - 0.38) - wp.sin(tmp))
    v0 = v2
    tmp = 0.17
    data[tid] = v0
